OL,4,CKiptum, 24, killed in car crash in
OL,5,CKenya
OL,7,FMarathon world record holder Kelvin
OL,8,FKiptum and his coach have died in an
OL,9,Faccident in Kenya, it has been
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FThe 24-year-old set a new world record
OL,13,Fof two hours and 35 seconds at the
OL,14,FChicago Marathon in October last year.
OL,16,FKenyan member of parliament Gideon
OL,17,FKimaiyo confirmed the pair's death in
OL,18,Fa statement on X, formerly known as
OL,19,FTwitter.
