OL,7,FMr Kimaiyo said: "It is with heavy
OL,8,Fhearts that we learn of the passing of
OL,9,FKelvin Kiptum, the world marathon
OL,10,Frecord holder, and his coach in a
OL,11,Ftragic accident along the Eldoret-
OL,12,FKaptagat road.
OL,14,F"Kelvin Kiptum was at the prime of his
OL,15,Fcareer, a legend in his own right.
OL,16,FIt's a tough one to take.
