OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with their families
OL,8,Fduring this incredibly difficult time.
OL,9,FThe people of Keiyo South are saddened
OL,10,Fby this loss. May their souls rest in
OL,11,Feternal peace."
OL,13,FDenis Muga, the area police chief for
OL,14,FKaptagat, said Kiptum was driving and
OL,15,Fonly one car was involved in the crash.
OL,17,FThe crash happened on a road between
OL,18,Fthe towns of Eldoret and Kaptagat in
OL,19,Fwestern Kenya.
