OL,7,FIt is high-altitude region which is
OL,8,Frenowned as a training base for top
OL,9,Fdistance runners from Kenya and across
OL,10,Fthe world.
OL,12,FIt is believed the crash happened at
OL,13,Faround 11pm.
OL,15,FKiptum also won the London Marathon in
OL,16,F2023 with a record time of two hours,
OL,17,Fone minute and 25 seconds.
