OL,7,FThe organisers of the London Marathon
OL,8,Fsaid on X: "We are shocked and deeply
OL,9,Fsaddened to hear the terrible news of
OL,10,Fthe death of marathon world record
OL,11,Fholder Kelvin Kiptum and his coach,
OL,12,FGervais Hakizimana.
OL,14,F"The thoughts of everyone at the TCS
OL,15,FLondon Marathon are with Kelvin's and
OL,16,FGervais' family and friends."
