OL,7,FWorld Athletics president Seb Coe
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are shocked and deeply
OL,9,Fsaddened to learn of the devastating
OL,10,Floss of Kelvin Kiptum and his coach,
OL,11,FGervais Hakizimana.
OL,13,F"On behalf of all at World Athletics
OL,14,Fwe send our deepest condolences to
OL,15,Ftheir families, friends, teammates and
OL,16,Fthe Kenyan nation.
