OL,7,F"It was only earlier this week in
OL,8,FChicago, the place where Kelvin set
OL,9,Fhis extraordinary marathon World
OL,10,FRecord, that I was able to officially
OL,11,Fratify his historic time.
OL,13,F"An incredible athlete leaving an
OL,14,Fincredible legacy, we will miss him
OL,15,Fdearly."
OL,17,FKiptum set the record for the fastest
OL,18,Fdebut marathon in history, crossing
OL,19,Fthe line in a course record of two
OL,20,Fhours, one minute and 53 seconds, at
OL,21,Fthe 2022 Valencia Marathon.
